name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond:
( t1.`OWNER_TYPE` = 'library'  AND  t1.`OWNER_SUBTYPE` = 'test_case'  AND  t1.`UPDATE_MAN` = #{ctx.sessioncontext.srfpersonid}  AND  exists(SELECT 1 FROM test_case t3 where t3.id = t1.owner_id and 
 t3.is_archived = 0 and t3.is_deleted =0) )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`CREATE_MAN`,
t1.`CREATE_TIME`,
t1.`ID`,
t1.`IDENTIFIER`,
t1.`IS_DELETED`,
t1.`NAME`,
t1.`OWNER_ID`,
t1.`OWNER_SUBTYPE`,
t1.`OWNER_TYPE`,
t1.`RECENT_PARENT`,
t1.`RECENT_PARENT_IDENTIFIER`,
t1.`RECENT_PARENT_NAME`,
concat(t1.`RECENT_PARENT_IDENTIFIER`,'-',t1.`IDENTIFIER`) AS `SHOW_IDENTIFIER`,
t1.`TYPE`,
t1.`UPDATE_MAN`,
t1.`UPDATE_TIME`
FROM `RECENT` t1
